>I have a question though. When I took out my trans, the bolts that held
>the RGB's on did not have any lock washers or lock plates.

It should have one or the other.  See the note on page H-2 3 of the '63-
'67 Bentley.  From chassis 1 197 853 (early November '63 production), the
lock plate (211 513 535) was replaced by a spring washer (N 12 232 1).

